data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom home nestled in the picturesque Berkshires neighborhood with sidewalk-lined streets and a community pool for residents to enjoy. Step inside to discover a floor plan designed for seamless entertaining. The formal dining room sets an elegant tone, while the kitchen boasts a large island perfect for gathering, connecting seamlessly to the family room. The light-filled morning room provides access to the back deck where you can enjoy the outdoors. Upstairs, a second-floor loft offers flexible space for various needs, alongside a convenient laundry area. Three guest bedrooms share a well-appointed main full bath, while the spacious owner's suite provides a private retreat with its own bath. The expansive unfinished walk-out basement offers ample storage and the potential to be transformed into additional living space, catering to your future needs and desires. Don't miss this opportunity to make this beautiful home your own!
